      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and is a rare find for any discerning buyer. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, showroom shine and zero imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car performs perfectly, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. You can expect a driving experience that feels as if the car just rolled off the assembly line. This is a collector-quality vehicle that requires absolutely no work and is ready for the road or a show floor.",
