    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep, mirror-like shine and zero imperfections, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state; the upholstery is unmarked, and every electronic component functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is impeccable, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and no signs of wear. A buyer can expect a vehicle that looks, smells, and drives like new, offering a true collector-grade experience.",
