      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$18,500 - Looking for a reliable and affordable daily driver? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next adventure! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a solid, dependable choice for anyone seeking great value. It\u2019s a practical option that\u2019s still got plenty of life left to give!",
      "price": 18500.0,
